    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera delivers a pure analog driving experience powered by a 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six. The powerplant features a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a clean bore scope, ensuring mechanical longevity. Mated to a crisp G97 6-speed manual transaxle, the drivetrain offers precise gear engagement and linear power delivery to the rear wheels. The chassis remains taut with PASM-equipped dampers and refreshed bushings, providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback. Recently serviced with a focus on cooling system integrity and oil analysis, this 911 is mechanically sorted and ready for the apex.",
      "price": 36500.0,
